---
import ServiceDetailLayout from "../../layouts/ServiceLayoutDetails.astro";
import { SERVICES } from "../../utils/constants";

const preWeddingService = SERVICES.find(
  (service) => service.slug === "pre-wedding"
);

// Additional metadata specifically for Pre-Wedding service
const serviceMetadata = {
  metaDescription:
    "Book premium themed sets for your Pre-Wedding Photography in Nagpur. Beautiful backdrops, props, and costumes available at Pixxel City Studio.",
  ogImage:
    "https://pixxelcity.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Vipin-Photography-2-Retro-Kitchen-scaled.jpg",
  canonicalUrl: "https://pixxelcity.com/services/pre-wedding",
  keywords:
    "pre-wedding photography sets, venue rental nagpur, photo studio sets, themed backdrops, pixxel city studio",
};

// Enhance the service object with additional metadata
const enhancedService = {
  ...preWeddingService,
  ...serviceMetadata,
  heroImage:
    "https://pixxelcity.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Vipin-Photography-2-Retro-Kitchen-scaled.jpg",
  process: [
    {
      title: "Initial Consultation",
      description:
        "We start with understanding your vision and preferred themes. Our team will help you select the perfect set options for your pre-wedding shoot.",
    },
    {
      title: "Set Selection",
      description:
        "Choose from our variety of themed sets including Light Room, Mexican Street, Retro Kitchen, French Window, French Cafe and more.",
    },
    {
      title: "Booking & Scheduling",
      description:
        "We'll help you reserve your preferred date and time slot, with package options to suit your requirements and budget.",
    },
    {
      title: "Day of Shoot",
      description:
        "Arrive at our studio where everything will be ready for you and your photographer. Enjoy access to our changing rooms, props, and refreshments.",
    },
    {
      title: "Set Changes & Support",
      description:
        "Our team provides support throughout your session, helping with set changes and ensuring you have everything needed for a successful shoot.",
    },
  ],
};
---

<ServiceDetailLayout service={enhancedService}>
  <Fragment slot="service-content">
    <h3>Premium Themed Sets for Your Pre-Wedding Photography</h3>

    <p>
      In recent years, pre-wedding photoshoots have become an essential part of
      the wedding journey for couples looking to capture beautiful memories
      before their big day. Finding the perfect locations and settings can be
      challenging and time-consuming.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Pixxel City Studio in Nagpur, we provide a convenient solution with our
      collection of professionally designed themed sets specifically created for
      pre-wedding photography. Our venue offers multiple backdrops under one
      roof, saving you time and ensuring stunning photos regardless of weather
      or season.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
      <img
        src="https://pixxelcity.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Vipin-Photography-2-Retro-Kitchen-scaled.jpg"
        alt="Retro Kitchen Pre-Wedding Photography Set"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
      <img
        src="https://pixxelcity.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/IMG_20241108_181458_617.webp"
        alt="Elegant Pre-Wedding Photography Set"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
    </div>

    <h3>Why Choose Pixxel City Sets for Your Pre-Wedding Shoot?</h3>

    <h4>Variety of Unique and Custom Sets</h4>

    <p>
      We offer a wide range of exotic and customized sets that truly reflect
      different styles and moods. Our themed environments like Light Room,
      Mexican Street, Retro Kitchen, French Window, and French Cafe provide
      perfect backdrops for your love story. Each set is carefully designed with
      attention to detail, ensuring your photos are one-of-a-kind.
    </p>

    <h4>Affordable and Convenient Packages</h4>

    <p>
      Our venue rental packages start from just ₹6,000, making
      professional-quality settings accessible for different budgets. We offer
      both general and advanced packages ranging from ₹6,000 to ₹16,000,
      allowing you to find an option that suits your needs without breaking the
      bank.
    </p>

    <h4>Exceptional Studio Amenities</h4>

    <p>
      At Pixxel City, we provide everything needed for a smooth and comfortable
      photoshoot experience. Our packages include access to changing/makeup
      rooms, complimentary water bottles, and appropriate props and costumes
      according to your chosen theme. Our friendly and professional staff is
      dedicated to making your pre-wedding shoot stress-free and enjoyable.
    </p>

    <blockquote
      class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg my-8 border-l-4 border-primary"
    >
      <p class="text-lg italic">
        "The themed sets at Pixxel City were incredible for our pre-wedding
        shoot! We were able to get photos in multiple settings all in one day.
        The Retro Kitchen set was our favorite, and the props really added
        character to our photos. Highly recommend this venue for any couple
        planning their pre-wedding photography."
      </p>
      <cite class="block mt-4 font-medium">— Neha & Rahul, Nagpur</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <h3>Our Popular Pre-Wedding Sets</h3>

    <h4>Retro Kitchen</h4>

    <p>
      A colorful, nostalgic kitchen setting perfect for playful couples who want
      to capture fun, domestic moments. Complete with vintage appliances and
      retro décor that photographs beautifully.
    </p>

    <h4>French Cafe</h4>

    <p>
      Create romantic Parisian vibes with our charming cafe setting featuring
      cafe tables, vintage lampposts, and European architectural elements that
      transport you to the streets of Paris.
    </p>

    <h4>Mexican Street</h4>

    <p>
      Vibrant and colorful set with authentic Mexican architecture, bright
      facades, and decorative elements that create a lively backdrop for couples
      seeking something unique and colorful.
    </p>

    <h4>Light Room</h4>

    <p>
      Modern and elegant setup featuring creative lighting installations perfect
      for dramatic and artistic photos with a contemporary edge.
    </p>

    <h3>Important Booking Information</h3>

    <p>
      When booking our studio for your pre-wedding shoot, please note that our
      packages include venue access, set usage, and basic amenities. You will
      need to arrange for your own photographer or can work with one of our
      recommended photography partners.
    </p>

    <p>
      We recommend booking at least 2-3 weeks in advance to secure your
      preferred date and time slot, especially during wedding season. A security
      deposit of ₹2,000 is required to confirm your booking, which is refundable
      after your session.
    </p>

    <h3>Book Your Pre-Wedding Set Today</h3>

    <p>
      Don't miss the opportunity to create stunning pre-wedding photos in our
      professionally designed sets. Contact Pixxel City Studio now to schedule a
      visit or make a booking. Let us help you create beautiful memories that
      you'll cherish for a lifetime.
    </p>
  </Fragment>
</ServiceDetailLayout>
